N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 20 ยง 561.15 - Diesel motor fuel

State Regulations

Except as otherwise provided, the provisions of this Part
pertain to motor fuel and do not specifically apply to diesel motor fuel. See
sections
1102
and
1111 (e)
of the Tax Law for
the imposition of the prepaid tax on diesel motor fuel. Notes
